Trigger → Sitemap Workflow
   → Generate sitemap.xml + robots.txt → Validate endpoints
       → IF success → Publish → Audit Log → Dashboard → Legacy Broadcast
       → IF failure → Survival Path:
           → Collect Logs → Validate Env → Retry
           → Incident Ticket → Rollback to last good sitemap
           → Legacy Broadcast → snapshot (sitemap hash + error logs)
